description:
This is a 32 minute workout called 'Restorative Yoga For Stress Relief | 30 Minute Practice' from the channel Jess Yoga.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: De-stress with this 30 minute calming yoga routine that includes gentle and simple full body stretches for relaxation. Each pose is held for around 2 minutes to give time for the body and mind to slow down, and to help reduce cortisol levels. 
Bring a pillow and/or block to this session, if you have them. No worries if not. 

Let me know how this practice goes for you in the comment section down below!

Namaste,
Jess
